      section.main
        ul#clues.ch-grid
          li 
            .ch-item.ch-img-2(style="margin-top: 30%;")
              .ch-info-wrap
                .ch-info
                  .ch-info-front.ch-img-2
                  .ch-info-back
                    h3 COMMUNISM
                    p
                      | One of these gentlemen had lived in Aberdeen House which is very close to our point of interest.
          li
            .ch-item.ch-img-3
              .ch-info-wrap
                .ch-info
                  .ch-info-front.ch-img-3
                  .ch-info-back
                    h3 BIG PUB
                    p
                      | If you are student you have definitely been to this pub which is 50 metere away from our POI!
          li
            .ch-item.ch-img-4(style="margin-top: 30%;")
              .ch-info-wrap
                .ch-info
                  .ch-info-front.ch-img-4
                  .ch-info-back
